\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{F\left(x\right)^{n+1}-1}{F\left(x\right)-1}=\frac{0-1}{F\left(x\right)-1}=\frac{1}{1-F\left(x\right)}$
\end_inset

